[all] Oh!

28:04.016 --> 28:07.728
But I'm just not allowed
to talk about it.

28:07.728 --> 28:10.606
Y'all think I'm whining every
time I talk about anything

28:10.606 --> 28:12.900
just because I come from money.

28:12.900 --> 28:14.985
But fuck that money.

28:14.985 --> 28:16.612
That money obviously
couldn't buy me

28:16.612 --> 28:19.490
a decent relationship
with my mom.

28:19.490 --> 28:22.159
And I know it's not the same
as, like, having a surgery

28:22.159 --> 28:23.786
or losing a job

28:23.786 --> 28:26.330
or putting up with white tears,

28:26.330 --> 28:28.749
but it still hurts.

28:28.749 --> 28:30.709
And I don't want to pretend
that it doesn't

28:30.709 --> 28:33.546
just because it doesn't seem
like a big deal to y'all.

28:33.546 --> 28:34.839
No, you don't have to pretend.

28:34.839 --> 28:37.299
- I'm still talking, Camille.
- Sorry.

28:37.299 --> 28:40.177
I will always be here
for you guys,

28:40.177 --> 28:43.013
but maybe check in on me
too sometimes.

28:43.013 --> 28:44.223
Yes.

28:44.223 --> 28:45.349
I'm sorry, Quinn.

28:45.349 --> 28:47.184
I apologize on behalf
of all of them

28:47.184 --> 28:50.187
'cause I always ask
about you, babe.

28:50.187 --> 28:52.356
I'm sorry, Quinn.

28:52.356 --> 28:55.443
You've been by my side
during this whole ordeal.

28:55.443 --> 28:57.570
See, it's like I always say.

28:57.570 --> 28:59.905
"You've got to check in
on your strong friends."

28:59.905 --> 29:02.741
Wait, you didn't make that up.

29:02.741 --> 29:04.743
That's like on 95%
of the internet.

29:04.743 --> 29:06.662
Right, but I always like it
and retweet it,

29:06.662 --> 29:08.038
- so it's the same.
- Oh, gosh, Angie.

29:08.038 --> 29:09.540
No.

29:09.540 --> 29:10.916
- I got you, my baby.
[Tye] Stop it.

29:10.916 --> 29:12.334
What--what are doing?

29:12.334 --> 29:14.253
I am trying to hook you up.

29:14.253 --> 29:15.963
She's in a hospital bed,
Angie.

29:15.963 --> 29:17.548
You ain't got to look like
what you've been through.

29:17.548 --> 29:19.842
- I'm just saying.
- [all chuckle]

29:19.842 --> 29:22.219
[Camille] While the "strong
Black woman" insignia

29:22.219 --> 29:25.139
charades as a compliment,

29:25.139 --> 29:26.974
it really pardons
the rest of the world

29:26.974 --> 29:28.350
of their responsibility

29:28.350 --> 29:31.312
to view the Black woman
as vulnerable,

29:31.312 --> 29:33.522
able to experience pain,

29:33.522 --> 29:35.191
capable of weakness,

29:35.191 --> 29:36.859
worthy of support,

29:36.859 --> 29:40.112
and unconditionally lovable.

29:40.112 --> 29:42.281
Until the Black woman
is allowed to reject

29:42.281 --> 29:43.908
this demand for strength,

29:43.908 --> 29:48.245
she'll never truly experience
her own humanity.

29:48.245 --> 29:51.582
Oh, good to see you awake
and in good spirits, Tyesha.

29:51.582 --> 29:53.501
Ooh, not the full
government name.

29:53.501 --> 29:54.919
Tye is fine.

29:54.919 --> 29:57.546
I had the surgery,
so I'm all good, right?

29:57.546 --> 29:59.840
I mean, I know there's
gonna be recovery time.

29:59.840 --> 30:01.675
Unfortunately, not quite.

30:01.675 --> 30:03.844
That cyst was just
the tip of the iceberg.

30:03.844 --> 30:06.597
You have several
medium and large

30:06.597 --> 30:09.850
fibroids and polyp
on your uterine lining.

30:09.850 --> 30:13.729
The good news is that we can
take care of everything at once

30:13.729 --> 30:15.105
with a hysterectomy.

30:15.105 --> 30:16.398
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

30:16.398 --> 30:18.275
Damn, that's a bit drastic,
don't you think?

30:18.275 --> 30:19.944
Of course it is.

30:19.944 --> 30:21.820
Well, I get the feeling

30:21.820 --> 30:23.697
you're not interested
in giving birth,

30:23.697 --> 30:26.534
and it really is the easiest
and most effective treatment.

30:26.534 --> 30:28.244
[scoffs]
Easiest for who?

30:28.244 --> 30:30.621
Just because I'm masc
doesn't mean I'm not a woman.

30:30.621 --> 30:32.581
And nobody asked you
for your feelings.

30:32.581 --> 30:34.458
[pager beeps]

30:34.458 --> 30:37.211
That would be the rest
of your labs, hang on.

30:37.211 --> 30:39.505
I am so sorry, Tye.

30:39.505 --> 30:41.465
I hate to be the voice
of reason, sweetheart,

30:41.465 --> 30:44.635
but maybe this is something
that we should all discuss

30:44.635 --> 30:46.595
before we rule it out
completely.

30:46.595 --> 30:49.014
I know I said
I don't want to have kids,

30:49.014 --> 30:52.059
but there's a difference
between not being able

30:52.059 --> 30:54.436
to have a baby
and not wanting to.

30:54.436 --> 30:56.105
True, and you know what?

30:56.105 --> 30:57.815
Who knows what
the future holds?

30:57.815 --> 31:00.067
You don't have
to make a decision

31:00.067 --> 31:01.277
with how you'd like to resolve

31:01.277 --> 31:02.528
the rest of the issues
right away,

31:02.528 --> 31:04.446
but sooner is better.

31:04.446 --> 31:07.700
Your labs look good enough
so I'm going to release you

31:07.700 --> 31:10.995
with some medication
and post-op instructions.

31:10.995 --> 31:13.956
Why don't you go home and talk
it over with your husband

31:13.956 --> 31:15.499
and get back to me
in a week or so?

31:15.499 --> 31:18.210
- This nigga.
- It is not 1950, okay?

31:18.210 --> 31:20.379
A woman does not need
to talk it over with a man

31:20.379 --> 31:23.257
when it comes to making
a decision about her body.

31:23.257 --> 31:25.676
I'm her husband.
Now what, asshole?

31:25.676 --> 31:26.927
Uh, you know what?
[chuckles]

31:26.927 --> 31:28.345
I am more her husband.

31:28.345 --> 31:30.598
Bitch, please, you're my wife,
and everyone knows this.

31:30.598 --> 31:31.724
Then who's husband am I?

31:31.724 --> 31:33.183
- Girl...
- I'm sorry.

31:33.183 --> 31:37.187
I don't want
to mis-pronoun anyone.

31:37.187 --> 31:39.523
Who is Brandon Jones?

31:39.523 --> 31:40.941
Nobody.

31:40.941 --> 31:42.901
That's the name that's
listed here on her HIPAA form

31:42.901 --> 31:45.988
and who gave us permission
to proceed with the surgery

31:45.988 --> 31:47.239
- while she was unconscious.
- What?

31:47.239 --> 31:48.532
What?
Oh, okay.

31:48.532 --> 31:50.618
So y'all are mixing up
paperwork now?

31:50.618 --> 31:52.411
I'm gonna have to call
my dad's attorney.

31:52.411 --> 31:54.371
This shit about
to be called Tye Memorial.

31:54.371 --> 31:56.206
Well, no, "Memorial" is like
when you're dead,

31:56.206 --> 31:57.625
- so maybe not that.
[Tye] Thank you, Camille.

31:57.625 --> 31:59.335
Don't undermine my point
in front of company.

31:59.335 --> 32:01.045
[knock on door]

32:04.465 --> 32:06.342
Hi, Tye.

32:06.342 --> 32:08.010
It's been a while.

32:08.010 --> 32:10.137
Huh, but who this, woman?

32:10.137 --> 32:11.805
Hi, Brandon.

32:11.805 --> 32:16.810
Uh, Brandon,
these are my friends.

32:16.810 --> 32:21.607
Friends,
this is Brandon Jones,

32:21.607 --> 32:23.025
my husband.

32:23.025 --> 32:25.944
[hip-hop music]

32:25.944 --> 32:28.447
[singer]

33:18.747 --> 33:20.124
Ah!
